{"word":"G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane - Understanding","slug":"G5424","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φρήν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phrḗn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>frane"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Understanding"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03C1;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03BD; - phre&#x0304;n</b> - <i>frane</i><p/>Probably from an obsolete <b>&#x03C6;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>phrao&#x0304;</b> (to <i>rein</i> in or <i>curb</i>; compare <a href=\"#/G5420\">G5420</a>); the <i>midrif</i> (as a <i>partition</i> of the body), that is, (figuratively and by implication of sympathy) the <i>feelings</i> (or sensitive nature; by extension [also in the plural] the <i>mind</i> or cognitive faculties): - understanding."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5426\">G5426</a>, <a href=\"#/G5427\">G5427</a>, <a href=\"#/G5428\">G5428</a>, <a href=\"#/G5429\">G5429</a>, <a href=\"#/G5430\">G5430</a>, <a href=\"#/G877\">G877</a>, <a href=\"#/G878\">G878</a>"}]}